ActDepartment of Citizenship and Immigration Act
SubjectCanada-New Brunswick Immigration Agreement
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration, pursuant to subsections 5(1) of the Department of Citizenship and Immigration Act and 8(1) of the Immigration and Refugee Protection Act, to enter into a CANADA-NEW BRUNSWICK IMMIGRATION AGREEMENT with the Government of New Brunswick. The effective period of the 2017 Agreement is 5 years, starting on the date that the 2017 Agreement is signed by both parties.
